replies.body:
Nice work, Random_Guy!
It really showcased the new walls map, Grotto Arena. It also demonstrated how on walls being a good teammate makes a difference in the outcome.
Also, if you want to see a player's health while you're spectating, you can check out their health along with their inventory when you right click. It should be in the upper left corner.
Next time, it would be fun to see a video of you in-game playing walls!
